 air as the inmates prepare for a Valentine\'s Day party; Red makes an intriguing new discovery. Larry asks Piper to be his prison mole.',7.89,'2014-06-06','/gotmC6GaCD4luNBetAUlky6wF2d.jpg',4,NULL),(246,'Comic Sans','1424','Piper starts a prison newsletter with the help of Healy and a few other inmates; Vee launches an entrepreneurial enterprise. ',7.78,'2014-06-06','/gGIph0QRjG59VCe2anuhCMWRm4n.jpg',4,NULL),(247,'Appropriately Sized Pots','1424','Piper faces a new backlash over special privileges; Caputo feels pressure to toughen up, resulting in administrative changes.',7.86,'2014-06-06','/nhiycDr1AMZOyMAWZhoFmK3iHSw.jpg',4,NULL),(248,'40 Oz. of Furlough','1424','Piper\'s relationship with Larry faces a real-world test; Red\'s effort to redeem herself is finally rewarded. A familiar figure returns to Litchfield.',7.96,'2014-06-06','/xUMh9zTpMfq6HOFFeMcYeNg7ZuA.jpg',4,NULL),(249,'Little Mustachioed Shit','1424','The guards get tougher in a bid to turn up prison contraband; a big, lingering secret is finally revealed.',8.03,'2014-06-06','/uL9hSfLBOEkGqcSf6N0jSnJtJV9.jpg',4,NULL),(250,'Take a Break from Your Values','1424','Piper is shocked at an unexpected change in her status; Soso\'s hunger strike attracts new support that takes on a religious fervor.',7.94,'2014-06-06','/rWECLIVLiEqnGyajfUjmEL4oYZp.jpg',4,NULL),(251,'It Was the Change','1424','Tensions run high as a prison power outage forces several issues to come to light. Piper finds herself compromised and is forced to think on her feet.',8.11,'2014-06-06','/yoGOVt01tQfNBz7GcmtQk1gzjcg.jpg',4,NULL),(252,'We Have Manners. We\'re Polite.','1424','Several futures hang in the balance as the inmates face and confront their worst nightmares: Life will never be the same again.',8.62,'2014-06-06','/bossMzlq0cPL8f2DVxYtpv58iHZ.jpg',4,NULL),(253,'Season 3','1424','New business interests, spiritual movements and parental problems upend lives and ignite power struggles among Litchfield\'s residents and guards.',8.04,'20