tion. A C.O. becomes suspicious about a broken door.',8.10,'2006-03-21','/bzxfRRDNaJFcyRtQEwhx59low2O.jpg',4,NULL),(534,'By the Skin and the Teeth','2288','As Lincoln is about to be executed, he briefly sees his father in the viewing room. A phone call from judge Kessler delays the execution. After reviewing the newly surfaced evidence, the judge orders the exhumation of Steadman\'s body.\n\nMichael creates a new, more dangerous, break-out plan, involving going through the prison yard. An accident puts Michael\'s new plan in danger.',8.02,'2006-03-28','/4CuelTzvqXpoNXdHkjs79Pw1jx3.jpg',4,NULL),(535,'Brother\'s Keeper','2288','Flashbacks shed light on the past actions that led to the incarceration of Lincoln, Sucre, T-Bag and C-Note. Basis of Michael\'s ingenious break-out plan are revealed. Dr. Tancredi memorizes how she ended up in Fox River State Penitentiary.',7.85,'2006-04-04','/iwSfygbc4TULWimQxGi48go2Zvm.jpg',4,NULL),(536,'J-Cat','2288','Lincoln is worried about Michael\'s sanity while Michael has trouble remembering some parts of the prison schematics. Sucre has to conceal the hole in the guard\'s break room. Warden Pope transfers Michael to solitary after he declines his request.',7.88,'2006-04-11','/k7hSD7OldbAz6lCIn6DJwaan8QY.jpg',4,NULL),(537,'Bluff','2288','In an effort to recreate the missing piece of the tattoo, Michael gets transferred to the psych ward, seeking the help of Haywire. T-Bag and C-Note have to join forces.',8.01,'2006-04-18','/cWtpyMrcqcRNVmlFRDhVRWKIFO6.jpg',4,NULL),(538,'The Key','2288','Michael must get the key to the infirmary and enlist the help of an old face, while Lincoln learns the identity of his kidnapper and another inmate learns of the escape.',8.02,'2006-04-25','/w0fNfB4TgBXcMDQwqaLUjfU2mZY.jpg',4,NULL),(539,'Tonight','2288','Westmoreland wants Michael to speed up the planned escape, and gets Bellick one step closer to unraveling it. Michael has to decide whether to involve Sara in the breakout plan. Tweener\'s devotion is 