 her overdose, Dr. Tancredi is in critical condition. \n\nA short-handed T-Bag faces the ultimate challenge.\n',7.97,'2006-08-22','/6ME8E7pEVDEmiBGhoamLkxC9Pqf.jpg',4,NULL),(544,'Otis','2288','Mahone tries to lure the escapees by targeting an imprisoned LJ. Michael and Lincoln come up with a plan to free LJ from jail. Sucre, Abruzzi and C-Note have a plan of their own, but only to break free of their pursuers.Meanwhile, Bellick and Warden Pope feel the heat following their unsuccessful attempts to capture the escapees.Tweener infiltrates a bunch of college students on their way to spring break.\n',7.88,'2006-08-29','/hOSV4OrsuSZSbLgsWxYY3Zy5iLf.jpg',4,NULL),(545,'Scan','2288','Michael and a wounded Lincoln try to outmaneuver Mahone, who is hot on their trail. Sara gets a surprise visit to her bedside. Following his suspension, Bellick recruits a resolute partner to aid in his quest to get the escapees behind the bars.Sucre and C-Note head out for their family reunions-regardless of being observed by the authorities.\n',7.91,'2006-09-05','/eOKlPXVTktCSafoBQLQSzFOMpbG.jpg',4,NULL),(546,'First Down','2288','Bellick, now teamed up with Michael, Lincoln and Nika, sets out to find the money stolen by Westmoreland during the 1971 skyjacking.\n\nKellerman targets Sara, who receives a long-awaited phone call. T-Bag gets a ride from an unsuspecting family. Abruzzi resumes the search for Fibonacci to settle the scores once and for all.\n',7.89,'2006-09-12','/hbg2Kcr7EodQ5ha6Uw0BzvBMJOs.jpg',4,NULL),(547,'Map 1213','2288','Michael and Lincoln are eager to locate the Double K ranch where Westmoreland hid his millions.\n\nSucre goes to Las Vegas to prevent Maricruz from marrying his cousin Hector. C-Note gets on a train.\n\nMahone is given an important package.\n',7.89,'2006-09-19','/sXU5TuCa3hD36dcYVTzIZBGkQaJ.jpg',4,NULL),(548,'Subdivision','2288','Mahone takes an interest in the story of DB Cooper.In their quest to find Westmoreland\'s treasure, Michael and Lincoln travel hous